  "Description": {
    "English": "A mounted laser system specifically designed for the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Nautilon Submarine</span>.<br><br>Fires a concentrated plasma beam towards the intended target, which is then ignited. Such a trigger mechanism allows the use of high-energy optical mining systems in a liquid medium.",
